column1: Nice to meet you as well.
Nothing. I exist here because I woke up here.

Correct. That means I make for a good
companion to people.
Are you human? Do you have a name?
Joker, do you know where this place—
Uh. I mean, who are you?

Anyway, who's this? Got a real funky
getup...
She popped out of a box.
そうか？　なんか子供じゃん。

Were you dumped down here by that
Alice girl too?

I just learned that I have no memories.
So I do not know.
Hey, you two come here for a second.
She said she doesn't have any memories?
She came out of a giant box!?
What kinda crazy shit is that? Way too weird...

She doesn't seem to be a Shadow, though...
She doesn't even seem hostile.
Whatever she is, we still gotta find a way out.

Nobody's solving any problems in this dump,
that's for sure.
If you're in trouble, I can help.

I am humanity's companion. My purpose is
to be helpful to humans.
Sooo, you wanna help us out?

Well, uh... We're lost. I guess we're lookin'
for a way outta here?

A way... Will reaching the surface solve your
problem of "a way outta here"?
I'm searching for "a way outta here."
Wha— Hey, don't go out there alone!
We can't just leave her here.

Right. She might be able to get us out of
this dump.

Right. She could be attacked by Shadows
any second now.
You sure about that? She's still super suspicious...
Buuut, I guess we shouldn't ditch her, either...
Hey! Hey, you better watch out for Shadows!
